1
00:00:19,262 --> 00:00:24,449
笙ｪThe whole world is lit up笙ｪ

2
00:00:24,450 --> 00:00:25,761
笙ｪBecause you exist笙ｪ

3
00:00:25,762 --> 00:00:27,841
笙ｪYou're always笙ｪ

4
00:00:27,842 --> 00:00:32,491
笙ｪSomewhere close, flying with me笙ｪ

5
00:00:32,492 --> 00:00:35,224
笙ｪGo to where the wind blows笙ｪ

6
00:00:35,225 --> 00:00:36,791
笙ｪHold tight笙ｪ

7
00:00:36,792 --> 00:00:42,581
笙ｪTo the ray of light that belongs to us笙ｪ

8
00:00:42,582 --> 00:00:48,020
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 15=

9
00:00:53,479 --> 00:00:56,320
(Who the heck is here so late at night?)

10
00:01:09,319 --> 00:01:10,160
It's me.

11
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:11,559
Boss.

12
00:01:12,359 --> 00:01:14,279
Why didn't you tell me
you were coming back?

13
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:20,039
I'm looking for a new way of creating.

14
00:01:21,439 --> 00:01:22,320
Boss,

15
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,559
are you unhappy?

16
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:28,639
No.

17
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:31,399
It's written all over your face.

18
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:33,320
I'm not stupid. I can tell.

19
00:01:33,719 --> 00:01:35,559
You've been by Ms. Mu's side
for so long.

20
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:38,679
Tonight is the first time you've come back.
Something must've happened.

21
00:01:39,319 --> 00:01:40,199
Boss,

22
00:01:40,359 --> 00:01:41,158
is it related

23
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:42,559
to that DNA test?

24
00:01:44,079 --> 00:01:45,718
The sample you gave me,

25
00:01:45,719 --> 00:01:46,880
whose was it?

26
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,839
Go get rest.

27
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,320
I want to be alone for a while.

28
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,358
Alright.

29
00:01:55,359 --> 00:01:56,520
I'll go to sleep then.

30
00:02:04,359 --> 00:02:06,080
(Why did it turn out like this?)

31
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:09,840
(How could she possibly be my sister?)

32
00:02:11,462 --> 00:02:14,861
笙ｪI close my innocent eyes笙ｪ

33
00:02:14,862 --> 00:02:17,819
笙ｪNo more parting by life or death笙ｪ

34
00:02:17,820 --> 00:02:22,100
笙ｪOnly mourning remains in my heart笙ｪ

35
00:02:23,420 --> 00:02:27,379
笙ｪDeeply trapped in
a vortex of mysteries笙ｪ

36
00:02:27,380 --> 00:02:31,339
笙ｪWading through the muddy waters
of hearts and times笙ｪ

37
00:02:31,340 --> 00:02:34,739
笙ｪReturning from the ashes
to craft the plan笙ｪ

38
00:02:34,740 --> 00:02:37,580
笙ｪFrom now on, no one can break it笙ｪ

39
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:45,260
笙ｪLove has vanished, hatred is spreading笙ｪ
(Shen Jibai)

40
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,680
Shen Jibai,

41
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,079
what are you running from?

42
00:02:51,919 --> 00:02:53,720
Even if it's a fake marriage,

43
00:02:54,199 --> 00:02:56,320
is it really that difficult for you?

44
00:02:57,840 --> 00:03:00,079
(Before I figure out
our true relationship,)

45
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:02,199
(we can't get married.)

46
00:03:02,380 --> 00:03:07,959
笙ｪThe green flower breaks in two,
our hearts will be together at last笙ｪ

47
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,239
(But now)

48
00:03:09,479 --> 00:03:11,720
(I've become an orphan.)

49
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,639
(You're not alone.)

50
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,739
(I'll always stay by your side.)

51
00:03:16,740 --> 00:03:18,911
笙ｪTo record your book of poetry笙ｪ

52
00:03:18,912 --> 00:03:21,638
笙ｪIf destined souls must part,
the broken mirror shall mend again笙ｪ

53
00:03:21,639 --> 00:03:22,680
Hello, Boss?

54
00:03:22,919 --> 00:03:23,679
Luyao,

55
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:25,160
please help me find out

56
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:27,239
where Shen Jibao has gone.

57
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,000
Alright.

58
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,639
Ms. Mu,

59
00:03:31,675 --> 00:03:33,598
Shen Jibai you're looking for
isn't here.

60
00:03:33,599 --> 00:03:35,079
I haven't been able to reach him.

61
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:37,079
My assistant said he saw him come here.

62
00:03:48,159 --> 00:03:50,479
(Luyao is certain Shen Jibai came here.)

63
00:03:51,159 --> 00:03:53,120
(But there's only Mr. Hong here.)

64
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,639
(Could it be...)

65
00:03:55,759 --> 00:03:57,519
Ms. Mu, please stop here.

66
00:04:00,919 --> 00:04:02,799
I've brought the complete proposal.

67
00:04:03,159 --> 00:04:05,239
I hope Mr. Hong can take a look at it.

68
00:04:05,639 --> 00:04:06,478
You can give it to me.

69
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:08,079
I'll pass it on to Mr. Hong.

70
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:11,639
Mr. Hong

71
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:13,840
still won't show his face?

72
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,400
You'll meet him if fate allows.

73
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:22,320
Boss.

74
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,661
This painting

75
00:04:39,662 --> 00:04:42,102
is very different
from Mr. Hong's previous style.

76
00:04:45,199 --> 00:04:47,159
Mr. Hong is trying something new.

77
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:49,719
What do you think, Ms. Mu?

78
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:50,639
Do you like it?

79
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,199
I like it very much.

80
00:04:52,959 --> 00:04:53,958
I can tell

81
00:04:53,959 --> 00:04:56,279
this is a bold breakthrough.

82
00:04:57,639 --> 00:04:58,839
If possible,

83
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,240
I'd like to auction it.

84
00:05:07,439 --> 00:05:08,800
Mr. Hong

85
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,800
is especially quiet today.

86
00:05:11,079 --> 00:05:12,800
Did something happen?

87
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,438
Mr. Hong

88
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:17,079
has recently been immersed
in exploring a new artistic style

89
00:05:17,199 --> 00:05:19,278
and doesn't want to talk to people.
It's normal.

90
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:20,240
You'll get used to it.

91
00:05:21,519 --> 00:05:22,360
Please.

92
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,680
(Mu Zhiyu,)

93
00:05:33,959 --> 00:05:35,800
(I still don't know how to face you.)

94
00:05:36,250 --> 00:05:39,274
笙ｪI wish to forget you笙ｪ

95
00:05:39,275 --> 00:05:44,599
笙ｪBut I'm powerless to keep living笙ｪ

96
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,480
You disappeared for two whole days.

97
00:05:46,839 --> 00:05:49,360
You didn't answer your phone
and didn't give any explanation.

98
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:51,279
What do you mean?

99
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:56,120
I've thought about it for a long time.
Now I can give you my answer.

100
00:05:58,240 --> 00:06:00,240
My answer is we cannot get married.

101
00:06:03,319 --> 00:06:04,440
Shen Jibai,

102
00:06:06,079 --> 00:06:08,000
so that's why you disappeared?

103
00:06:09,079 --> 00:06:10,800
You're so full of yourself.

104
00:06:11,199 --> 00:06:12,359
I, Mu Zhiyu,

105
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:16,679
have plenty of people I could marry.
You're not the only option.

106
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:20,811
笙ｪLooking up,
there's the beautiful starry sky笙ｪ

107
00:06:20,812 --> 00:06:23,518
笙ｪBut you forgot to teach me笙ｪ

108
00:06:23,519 --> 00:06:25,318
(Zhiyu, don't resent me.)

109
00:06:25,319 --> 00:06:27,159
(Once I find out the truth,)

110
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,719
(if fate is kind to us,)

111
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:31,480
(I'll do everything in my power
to protect you for the rest of your life.)

112
00:06:33,639 --> 00:06:35,519
Take this bowl of bird's nest soup
to Ms. Mu.

113
00:06:35,879 --> 00:06:36,759
Remember.

114
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,959
You must watch her finish it.

115
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:39,839
Yes.

116
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:49,440
(I don't have time to watch
your little quarrel.)

117
00:06:49,879 --> 00:06:51,920
(Once everything is in place,)

118
00:06:52,279 --> 00:06:54,279
(you'll have no choice
but to get married.)

119
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,839
Captain Shen.

120
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,839
It seems something happened
to Mu Zhiyu.

121
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:05,360
You're so kind as to warn me?

122
00:07:05,639 --> 00:07:07,040
Believe what you want.

123
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:26,999
Zhiyu,

124
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:27,959
what's wrong with you?

125
00:07:48,225 --> 00:07:50,845
笙ｪWhatever happens笙ｪ

126
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:54,745
笙ｪGod knows I've tried笙ｪ

127
00:07:56,759 --> 00:07:57,759
(No.)

128
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:00,159
(Before I find out the truth
about our identities,)

129
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,480
(I cannot make a mistake.)

130
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:03,999
笙ｪHand on the weapon笙ｪ

131
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,000
Mu Zhiyu.

132
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,480
Zhiyu.

133
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,759
Wake up.

134
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,360
I'll take you to see a doctor.

135
00:08:27,500 --> 00:08:31,299
笙ｪAin't no fire, fire笙ｪ

136
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:34,236
笙ｪNever surrender to the cold笙ｪ

137
00:08:34,237 --> 00:08:38,124
笙ｪAin't no fire, fire笙ｪ

138
00:08:38,125 --> 00:08:41,367
笙ｪCan hurt you like your own笙ｪ

139
00:08:41,368 --> 00:08:46,513
笙ｪSo I let it burn, burn笙ｪ

140
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,160
Wake up.

141
00:08:55,399 --> 00:08:56,839
I'm taking you to see a doctor.

142
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,520
Doctor, how's she?

143
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:05,719
I've prescribed some medicine
to help her metabolism.

144
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:07,760
Once she wakes up, she should be fine.

145
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:15,079
Here's the test report you requested.

146
00:09:19,399 --> 00:09:21,558
(Blood type: O)
Her physical indicators are all healthy.

147
00:09:21,559 --> 00:09:22,758
(Zhiyu is blood type O?)

148
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:23,959
Don't worry too much.

149
00:09:24,559 --> 00:09:25,640
Wait.

150
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:32,199
Are you sure
this is Ms. Mu's rest report?

151
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,040
Yes.

152
00:09:33,759 --> 00:09:36,959
And our testing equipment
is the most advanced available.

153
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,839
You can rest assured.

154
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:43,040
(Mu Chenzhou is type AB.)

155
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:45,040
(Blood type: O)
(Mu Zhiyu is type O.)

156
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:48,640
(That means she can't possibly be
Mu Chenzhou's daughter.)

157
00:09:49,175 --> 00:09:51,239
(Then we aren't siblings.)

158
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:55,879
(Zhiyu, we can get married.)

159
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:13,599
(The Mu Group heiress falls for
her personal bodyguard.)

160
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:16,959
(They secretly live together
and she gets pregnant out of wedlock.)

161
00:10:21,062 --> 00:10:23,507
(The Mu family must have a real headache.
The heiress is pregnant.)

162
00:10:24,039 --> 00:10:24,758
(How did)

163
00:10:24,759 --> 00:10:26,560
(so many negative reports
appear so quickly?)

164
00:10:27,399 --> 00:10:29,520
(It must be Xu Mingzhu behind all this.)

165
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,119
I'm fine.

166
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,400
Let's go to the office first.

167
00:10:45,037 --> 00:10:49,267
笙ｪLight comes beaming in笙ｪ

168
00:10:49,407 --> 00:10:53,776
笙ｪLanding on my skin笙ｪ

169
00:10:53,777 --> 00:10:58,267
笙ｪWarms the space you left behind笙ｪ

170
00:11:02,487 --> 00:11:06,426
笙ｪShadows move around笙ｪ

171
00:11:06,427 --> 00:11:11,036
笙ｪAwake, racing thoughts笙ｪ

172
00:11:11,037 --> 00:11:15,567
笙ｪTry to keep the memories safe笙ｪ

173
00:11:19,167 --> 00:11:24,957
笙ｪDon't slip away笙ｪ

174
00:11:27,407 --> 00:11:31,976
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

175
00:11:31,977 --> 00:11:36,376
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

176
00:11:36,377 --> 00:11:40,697
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

177
00:11:40,717 --> 00:11:44,697
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

178
00:11:45,167 --> 00:11:49,476
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

179
00:11:49,477 --> 00:11:53,806
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

180
00:11:53,807 --> 00:11:58,116
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ

181
00:11:58,117 --> 00:12:04,267
笙ｪI'm all yours, all yours笙ｪ
